      "title": "IOC suspends fuel supply to filling stations",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the Ceylon Indian Oil Company has suspended the release of fuel to petrol stations until next Monday (11th).",
        "The company mentions that fuel will be supplied to factories on Saturdays and Sundays and the release of fuel to filling stations will start again from Monday."
      ],
